hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.exec

Class NumberOperations

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.exec.NumberOperations

  • public class NumberOperations
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides basic binary arithmetic operations over Integers and Doubles. If both operands are Integers result will also be an Integer; otherwise it will be a Double. Operands and result are of type Number.
